title: Grateful Dead Live at Robert F. Kennedy Stadium on 1986-07-06
lineage: Charlie Miller DSD Transfer: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC 24/96  Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Flac 24/96
description:
Set I
Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Row Jimmy, Cassidy, Althea, Let It Grow
Set II
Saint Of Circumstance-> Iko Iko, Looks Like Rain> He's Gone> Drums> Space> Stella Blue> Throwing Stones> Not Fade Away; E: Brokedown Palace
Set III
 
Comment
Dylan, Petty & Heartbreakers Opened.
